<section class="insurance-block">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="insurance-content-wrapper">
            <div class="insurance-text">
                <h2>Navigating Your Insurance Claim Post-SB 2A</h2>
                <p class="lead-text">
                    Florida's Senate Bill 2A has changed how mold claims are
                    handled. Direct billing is complex, and documentation is now
                    your most critical asset.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We provide the <strong>Certified Mold Protocol</strong> and <strong
                        >forensic moisture logs</strong
                    > your insurance carrier demands to approve coverage. We don't
                    just clean; we document everything to protect your financial
                    interests.
                </p>
                <div class="checklist">
                    <div class="check-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>Detailed Moisture Logs</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="check-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>Thermal Imaging Evidence</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="check-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>Certified Remediation Protocol</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="insurance-visual">
                <div class="document-card">
                    <div class="doc-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="doc-title">Official Mold Assessment Report</div>
                    <div class="doc-status">SB 2A COMPLIANT</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .insurance-block {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b2545 0%, #1a3c6e 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 5rem 1rem;
    }

    .insurance-content-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 4rem;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .insurance-text {
        flex: 1;
    }

    .insurance-text h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .lead-text {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .checklist {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .check-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .check-item i {
        color: #4cd137;
    }

    .insurance-visual {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .document-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #333;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        max-width: 300px;
        transform: rotate(2deg);
    }

    .doc-icon {
        font-size: 4rem;
        color: #0b2545;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .doc-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .doc-status {
        background: #e74c3c;
        color: white;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .insurance-content-wrapper {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .checklist {
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .check-item {
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }
</style>
